Yes, sir. I'll put that
right through. Connecting now.

515
00:56:06,446 --> 00:56:08,447
Operator. Direct me to the War Ministry.

516
00:56:08,531 --> 00:56:10,199
General Olbricht's office.
One moment, please.

517
00:56:10,283 --> 00:56:12,326
Yes, sir.
Connecting now.

518
00:56:16,206 --> 00:56:17,289
General Olbricht's office.

519
00:56:17,415 --> 00:56:18,457
Himmler's not
in the briefing.

520
00:56:18,541 --> 00:56:20,167
I'm ready to arm.
Permission to proceed.

521
00:56:20,460 --> 00:56:22,211
Hold the line.

522
00:56:22,295 --> 00:56:26,173
Stauffenberg says Himmler's not at
the briefing. He wants to proceed.

523
