What do you say?

531
00:57:08,341 --> 00:57:09,758
I say do it.

532
00:57:10,635 --> 00:57:12,010
Attention!

533
00:57:47,046 --> 00:57:50,591
Whatever it was, Colonel,
I hope it was important.

534
00:57:52,927 --> 00:57:55,512
Colonel? Your bag.

535
00:58:20,038 --> 00:58:23,582
This has been a drill!
You're dismissed!

536
