Damn near cost me
my commission.

538
00:58:32,759 --> 00:58:35,385
And what in God's name made you
think you even had the authority?

539
00:58:35,470 --> 00:58:36,887
It was only a drill,
an exercise.

540
00:58:36,971 --> 00:58:39,765
Oh, don't lie, Olbricht!
Not to me.

541
