a target on my back.

547
00:58:51,194 --> 00:58:55,155
If I so much as sense you trying
to move the Reserve Army again,

548
00:58:55,240 --> 00:58:58,075
I will personally
have you both arrested.

549
00:59:00,286 --> 00:59:03,163
Do I make myself
abundantly clear?

550
00:59:03,248 --> 00:59:05,040
Yes, sir.
Yes, sir.

551
00:59:09,462 --> 00:59:11,505
Heil Hitler.
Heil Hitler.

552
00:59:13,633 --> 00:59:15,926
I'll hear you
say it, Colonel.

553
00:59:25,103 --> 00:59:26,520
Heil Hitler!

554
