be difficult. Of course.

622
01:06:30,069 --> 01:06:31,653
Plenty of time.

623
01:06:56,637 --> 01:06:59,347
Get the car.
But, sir...

624
01:06:59,432 --> 01:07:02,100
I have everything
I need. Get the car.

625
01:07:31,088 --> 01:07:32,797
I can manage this.

626
01:07:45,811 --> 01:07:47,645
Where are they going?
It's too hot.

627
