our troops have already been
pushed back to the Polish border.

646
01:09:26,662 --> 01:09:28,204
Conference hut.

647
01:09:28,289 --> 01:09:31,833
This, compounded with the
loss of the 4th Army in Minsk,

648
01:09:31,959 --> 01:09:34,878
threatens the entire
