01:10:43,989 --> 01:10:46,032
One thing is certain,

667
01:10:46,116 --> 01:10:49,869
the Red Army will continue
an aggressive push west,

668
01:10:49,954 --> 01:10:50,995
even at the expense...

669
01:10:55,584 --> 01:10:57,502
In order to
rebuild at this...

