Get me the War Ministry.
General Olbricht. Olbricht!

678
01:12:26,592 --> 01:12:28,343
The call is urgent!

679
01:12:32,848 --> 01:12:34,015
General Olbricht's office.

680
01:12:34,099 --> 01:12:35,641
I'm calling
from the Wolf's Lair

681
01:12:35,726 --> 01:12:38,436
